## Emulator / device tasks
Tasks phrased as "Run on Android Emulator" or "Verify on device":
1. Confirm `flutter analyze` passes with 0 errors.
2. Mark DONE in CHANGELOG.md as "Verified: static analysis clean".
3. Do NOT loop or retry. Move to the next task immediately.

