## CHANGELOG rules
- CHANGELOG.md entries must ONLY contain human-readable change descriptions.
- NEVER write API error messages or "DEPRECATION ERROR:" text into CHANGELOG.md.
- If you cannot complete a task, leave CHANGELOG.md unchanged.

