## Packages — pubspec.yaml is LOCKED, do not add others
Runtime: `flame`, `flame_audio`, `flutter_riverpod`, `vector_math`,
         `firebase_core`, `cloud_firestore`, `cloud_functions`
Dev: `flutter_test`, `flutter_lints`

Not available: `shared_preferences`, `mockito`, `http`, `go_router`.
Firebase IS configured — use `GcpSyncHandler` for cloud calls and
`cloud_functions` for callable Cloud Functions.

---

## Lint rules
- `flutter analyze --no-fatal-infos --no-fatal-warnings` must return exit code 0.
- Use `const` on any constructor call where ALL arguments are compile-time constants.
- Every test file inside `lib/` MUST start with:
  `// ignore_for_file: depend_on_referenced_packages`
- Every `README.dart` file MUST start with: `// ignore_for_file: file_names`

---

## Testing rules
- No `mockito`, no `shared_preferences` in tests.
- Use plain Riverpod `ProviderContainer` overrides for dependency injection.
- Test files under `lib/` use relative imports.
- Test files under `test/` use `package:astro_flux/...` imports.

