## What NOT to do
- Do not add packages without checking pub.dev.
- Do not commit secrets or .env files.
- Do not use GoRouter or named routes — this is a game, not a multi-screen app.
- Do not render game state using Material widgets inside the Flame canvas.
- Do not invent model fields — use only what is listed in "Current model schema".
- Do not write stub method bodies. See anti-stub rule at the top of this file.
